main event: A witness reported seeing two unidentified flying objects in New Carlisle, Ohio on December 5, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for about 20 minutes,The objects moved in an erratic course,The report was received by Project Blue Book in 1968,There was only one confirmed witness to the event,No photographs or physical evidence were found.
witness description: Male, age 21, resident of New Carlisle
